<br />

<br />
My first time at this camp and had heard some decent stuff dropped. So I loaded up my standard Swarm/charm kiting lineup . . and proceeded to discover MANY of these guys could not be charmed . ./boggle.
<br />

<br />
Faded . . and thought, what the heck, they dont seem to hit too hard, and are all kinda little, I'll give AE a try.
<br />

<br />
Worked great here . . whereas, I get THRASHED trying to AE Hobgoblins in PoN. . . 
<br />

<br />
Is AE easier here for other folks? Is it because of the mob type, or The  Zone???
<br />

<br />
Any thoughts?. ..  . 
<br />
I do wish there were some other , comparable mobs nearby, since  respawn takes WAYYYY  too long.</span></td>
