It is too efficient.
<br />

<br />
The reason the camp is popular is the named spawn. She has a chance to spawn from any of the restless soul placeholders so long as she is not already spawned.
<br />

<br />
By stretching out the kill times you have a chance for more than one named to pop on a cycle.
<br />

<br />
Look at the restless souls too. Sex is important.
<br />
Boy ghosts are charmable, girl ghosts are not.
